{%- style -%}
  .lab-results-table {
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 0;
    width: 100%;
    border: 2px solid rgb(108, 117, 155);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .lab-results-table th {
    background-color: rgb(108, 117, 155);
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: left;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }
  .lab-results-table th:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  .lab-results-table td {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(108, 117, 155);
    border-right: 1px solid rgb(108, 117, 155);
  }
  .lab-results-table td:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  .lab-results-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .lab-results-table tr:nth-child(even) {
    background-color: white;
  }
{%- endstyle -%}

<div class="mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 py-12 mt-10">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex md:flex-row gap-8 md:px-8 items-start py-12">
    <div class=" w-full md:w-[50%] flex-shrink-0">
      <img 
        src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/cn55vbgx/production/d3a5908f09401920248f5c6451561e3c2133ee0c-1300x838.jpg?rect=1,0,1299,838&w=1000&h=645&q=80&fit=max&auto=format"
        alt="BambooTek Lab Results"
        class="w-full h-[300px] object-cover rounded-xl border-2 border-core"
      >
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 py-2">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-core mb-6">{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 space-y-7 text-core">
        <p>The BambooTek® Diaper is made of 88% plant-based, biodegradable materials. The superstar: it's powered by our proprietary tree-free, totally chlorine free (TCF) BambooTek® core (100% bamboo pulp and superabsorbent polymer).</p>
        
        <p>The core is wrapped in performance-driven non-woven fabrics (polypropylene and polyethylene), printed with water-soluble, toxin-free inks, and held together with elastic (spandex, polypropylene and polyethylene).</p>
        
        <p>Testing for chemical compounds and performance versus the competition was completed by an independent laboratory in October 2021. It's been proven to be free of, below detectable, or significantly below allowed levels (when regulation exists) for nearly 200 chemicals that may be considered toxic or harmful for use, including the list below.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="overflow-x-auto mt-36">
    <!-- Single table for Mobile -->
    <div class="block lg:hidden">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
        <table class="min-w-full lab-results-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th class="rounded-tl-lg">Volatile Organic Components & Compounds Content</th>
              <th class="rounded-tr-lg">STATUS</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {%- for i in (1..20) -%}
              {%- capture row_name -%}row_{{ i }}_name{%- endcapture -%}
              {%- capture row_status -%}row_{{ i }}_status{%- endcapture -%}
              <tr>
                <td class="text-core">{{ section.settings[row_name] }}</td>
                <td class="text-core">{{ section.settings[row_status] }}</td>
              </tr>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!--Desktop tables-->
    <div class="hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-4 md:px-8">
      <!-- First table -->
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
        <table class="min-w-full lab-results-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th class="rounded-tl-lg">Volatile Organic Components & Compounds Content</th>
              <th class="rounded-tr-lg">STATUS</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {%- for i in (1..10) -%}
              {%- capture row_name -%}row_{{ i }}_name{%- endcapture -%}
              {%- capture row_status -%}row_{{ i }}_status{%- endcapture -%}
              <tr>
                <td class="text-core">{{ section.settings[row_name] }}</td>
                <td class="text-core">{{ section.settings[row_status] }}</td>
              </tr>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <!-- Second table -->
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
        <table class="min-w-full lab-results-table">
          <tbody>
            {%- for i in (11..20) -%}
              {%- capture row_name -%}row_{{ i }}_name{%- endcapture -%}
              {%- capture row_status -%}row_{{ i }}_status{%- endcapture -%}
              <tr>
                <td class="text-core">{{ section.settings[row_name] }}</td>
                <td class="text-core">{{ section.settings[row_status] }}</td>
              </tr>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

